name: Enemy Zero
description:
This script will install "Enemy Zero" CD edition with support for modern computer configuration. 
During install please let all options by default.
Thanks to the people who contributed to play this game in the best conditions.

insert-disc.description: Please insert "Enemy Zero" CD1 and press autodetect

task.description: Running setup of the game. Just proceed and keep all settings at their defaults
task.name: wineexec

content:
files:
- dxwnd: https://liquidtelecom.dl.sourceforge.net/project/dxwnd/Latest%20build/v2_05_23_build.rar
game:
  exe: drive_c/Program Files (x86)/Konami/Silent Hill 2 - Directors Cut/sh2pc.exe
  prefix: $GAMEDIR
installer:
- task:
    arch: win64
    description: Preparing "Enemy Zero" folder
    name: create_prefix
    prefix: $GAMEDIR
- insert-disc:
    description: Please insert "Enemy Zero" CD1 and press autodetect
    requires: $DISC/ezero/e0l.exe
- task:
    args: /desktop=EnemyZero,1024x780 $DISC/ezero/e0l.exe
    description: Running setup of the game. Just proceed and keep all settings at
      their defaults
    executable: $GAMEDIR/drive_c/windows/explorer.exe
    name: wineexec
- extract:
    dst: $GAMEDIR/drive_c/dxwnd
    file: dxwnd
- write_config:
    data:
      target:
        cdvol0: 100
        codepage0: 0
        coord0: 3
        country0: 0
        dflag0: 0
        dflagb0: 0
        fakec0: None
        faked0: None
        filterid0: 0
        flag0: 673185824
        flagg0: 1207959568
        flagh0: 22
        flagi0: 138412036
        flagj0: 4224
        flagk0: 66560
        flagl0: 0
        flagm0: 65536
        flagn0: 17825796
        flago0: 0
        flagp0: 8192
        flagq0: 0
        icon0: 
        initresh0: 600
        initresw0: 800
        initts0: 0
        lang0: 0
        launchpath0: C:\SEGA\VFPC\VFPC.EXE
        maxddinterface0: 7
        maxfps0: 0
        maxres0: -1
        module0: null
        monitorid0: -1
        notes0: null
        opengllib0: null
        path0: C:\SEGA\VFPC\VFPC.EXE
        posx0: 50
        posy0: 50
        registry0: null
        renderer0: 3
        scanline0: 0
        sizx0: 800
        sizy0: 600
        slowratio0: 2
        startfolder0: C:\SEGA\VFPC\
        swapeffect0: 0
        tflag0: 0
        title0: Virtua FIghter
        ver0: 0
        winver0: 0
      window:
        exepath: C:\SEGA\VFPC\
        expert: 1
        exportpath: C:\dxwnd\exports\
        posx: 786
        posy: 506
    file: $GAMEDIR/drive_c/dxwnd/dxwnd.ini
- task:
    arch: win64
    key: csmt
    name: set_regedit
    path: HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Wine\Direct3D\
    prefix: $GAMEDIR
    type: REG_DWORD
    value: '00000000'
- task:
    arch: win64
    key: background
    name: set_regedit
    path: HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Control Panel\Colors\
    prefix: $GAMEDIR
    type: REG_SZ
    value: 0 0 0
wine:
  Desktop: true
